headline: Did ASGN's Multi-Year Partnership Just Shift Salesforce's (CRM) AI-Driven Investment Narrative?
summary: ASGN Incorporated recently announced a multi-year partnership with Salesforce, integrating Salesforce's Agentforce to drive automation and AI-driven innovation across its digital engineering and client service offerings. This collaboration highlights Salesforce's expanding role in powering enterprise-level AI adoption, as Agentforce is leveraged to transform core workflows and accelerate time to value for commercial and government clients.
